   "source": [
    "Pyenv:\n",
    "\n",
    "It is a tool that helps install,manage and switch between multiple versions of python in the same system\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "51727432-bbe1-4ce8-bdc3-5eb9574f8d29",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#command to install particular version\n",
    "\n",
    "pyenv install 3.12.2\n",
    "\n",
    "# to set it as global version\n",
    "pyenv global 3.12.2 \n",
    "\n",
    "# to set it for local version\n",
    "cd my_project\n",
    "pyenv local 3.9.18\n",
    "\n",
    "# to check current version\n",
    "pyenv version"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f0e5d7bc-7646-485d-8065-041f6ef57f95",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Jupyter Lab\n",
    "\n",
    "It is a advanced version of jupyter notebook. Lab has better ui, provides option to handle multiple files, extensions can be added."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "027c79cf-c37d-4c0a-a2cc-56c99589a200",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "pip install jupyterlab\n",
    "\n",
    "to run: jupyter lab"
   ]
  }
 ],
